217;s heavyweights, including the Godfather of Web Standards, Jeff Zeldman. Its focus on design and UX is one of the reasons we&#8217;re so excited about it.</p>\n<p>Each year, <a href="https://twitter.com/gavinelliott" target="_blank">Gavin</a> (its founder) goes the extra mile to expand, brighten and make it more engaging, and this year will be no different. In fact back in 2012, we made the trek from South Africa to Newcastle to attend the first event and left with relationships and opportunities that we still have to this day.</p>\n<blockquote><p>At Industry, every year is different. Our Industry moves quickly and I spend months out of every year working with speakers and curating content so that every attendee can get practical takeaways from the day. Every year we meet to learn something new.<br />\n<cite>Gavin Elliott</cite></p></blockquote>\n<p>You can check out the amazing <a href="http://2016.industryconf.com/" target="_blank">speaker list</a> and <a href="http://2016.industryconf.com/" target="_blank">event details</a> here.</p>\n<h3>We&#8217;re giving away two tickets!</h3>\n<p>With the conference now being an established part of the web conference circuit, we have teamed up with Gavin to give away two IndustryConf tickets to this year&#8217;s event, valued at £300.</p>\n<p><strong>To enter is really simple:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Leave a comment on our blog with a reason why you think you should win the free tickets</li>\n<li>Don&#8217;t forget to leave your twitter name in the comment so we can contact when you win</li>\n</ol>\n<p>The winner will be announced on our twitter account next week! Good luck!</p>\n<p><em>Please make sure that you are able to attend the conference on the 20th of April 2016. We really want these tickets to go to someone who is excited and interested by what IndustryConf has to offer.</em></p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.layerswp.com/2016/03/win-two-free-tickets-to-industry-conference/">Win Two Free Tickets to Industry Conf!</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.layerswp.com">Layers</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:81:"http://www.layerswp.com/2016/03/win-two-free-tickets-to-industry-conference/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2:"10";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:45:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:86:"Our First Theme of 2016 is Live, Say Hello to Crafthouse a WooCommerce Furniture Theme";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:88:"http://www.layerswp.com/2016/03/our-first-theme-of-2016-is-live-say-hello-to-crafthouse/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:96:"http://www.layerswp.com/2016/03/our-first-theme-of-2016-is-live-say-hello-to-crafthouse/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Wed, 02 Mar 2016 10:52:20 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"News";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"themes";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"http://www.layerswp.com/?p=2390";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:536:"<p>This one has been a long time in the making but we''re super excited to launch it. Crafthouse is a WooCommerce Furniture Theme designed for the contemporary furniture company looking for a fresh and modern look for their website.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.layerswp.com/2016/03/our-first-theme-of-2016-is-live-say-hello-to-crafthouse/">Our First Theme of 2016 is Live, Say Hello to Crafthouse a WooCommerce Furniture Theme</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.layerswp.com">Layers</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"David Perel";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2469:"<p><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/crafthouse-woocommerce-furniture-theme/14542098?ref=obox">Crafthouse</a> has been a project that we&#8217;ve been busy with since December of 2015. A furniture theme designed by an incredibly talented South African, <a href="http://www.ianroblambert.com/">Ian Lambert</a>, we wanted something that fits perfectly into Layers&#8217; ability to create different layouts with the click of a button.</p>\n<p>When Ian presented us with the initial designs we were so happy that we jumped directly into the conversion phase. The result is what you see here, a WooCommerce theme aimed at modern furniture companies who are looking for a fresh look for their website.</p>\n<p><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/crafthouse-woocommerce-furniture-theme/full_screen_preview/14542098?ref=obox" target="_blank" rel="attachment wp-att-2391"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-2391" src="http://www.layerswp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/crafthouse-screenshots.jpg" alt="crafthouse-screenshots" width="1000" height="339" srcset="http://www.layerswp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/crafthouse-screenshots-300x102.jpg 300w, http://www.layerswp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/crafthouse-screenshots-768x260.jpg 768w, http://www.layerswp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/crafthouse-screenshots.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></a></p>\n<p>We love it and know you will too with it&#8217;s minimal look, sharp typography and inspiring demo content.</p>\n<p>As with any Layers theme created by our team, we have made sure it works seamlessly with all our plugins and has been tested with all the options available in the free version of Layers. Dynamic header layouts, multiple widgets and the 100&#8217;s of different Content Widget combos have been factored into it&#8217;s design.</p>\n<p>Crafthouse can be bought on Themeforest for $46 and comes packaged with <a href="http://www.layerswp.com/storekit/">StoreKit</a> absolutely free. <a href="http://themeforest.net/item/crafthouse-woocommerce-furniture-theme/full_screen_preview/14542098?ref=obox">Check out the demo</a> and let us know what you think in the comments!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.layerswp.com/2016/03/our-first-theme-of-2016-is-live-say-hello-to-crafthouse/">Our First Theme of 2016 is Live, Say Hello to Crafthouse a WooCommerce Furniture Theme</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.layerswp.com">Layers</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:93:"http://www.layerswp.com/2016/03/our-first-theme-of-2016-is-live-say-hello-to-crafthouse/feed/";s:7:"