h="300" height="147" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/instalasi-pipa-3-b.png" />																					\n\nStep 4																									\n																																		Taruh pasir hingga 1/3 – 2/3 dari diameter pipa – tergantung dari tipe yang diusulkan konsultan (Unsupported, Haunch Supported, atau Side supported), lalu padatkan pasir pada sisi pipa\n\n<img width="300" height="148" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/instalasi-pipa-4-b.png" />																					\n\nStep 5																									\n																																		Timbun sisa galianpipa dan padatkan kembali.Bilamana pipatertanam di posisi yang cukup dalam, sebisa mungkin pemadatan dilakukan setiap40 – 60 cm\n\n<img width="300" height="143" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/instalasi-pipa-5-b.png" />																					\n\n', 'Handling', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '127-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-15 11:09:58', '2016-03-15 11:09:58', 'a:4:{s:7:"post_id";i:127;s:9:"post_hash";s:44:"layers_page_90818dd3359f322148b6193ae30baea2";s:10:"post_title";s:8:"Handling";s:11:"widget_data";a:1:{s:23:"obox-layers-builder-127";a:9:{s:23:"layers-widget-column-12";a:4:{s:6:"design";a:6:{s:6:"layout";s:12:"layout-boxed";s:9:"liststyle";s:9:"list-grid";s:6:"gutter";s:2:"on";s:5:"fonts";a:3:{s:5:"align";s:11:"text-center";s:4:"size";s:6:"medium";s:5:"color";s:7:"#ffffff";}s:10:"background";a:4:{s:5:"color";s:0:"";s:5:"image";s:59:"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/1.jpg";s:6:"repeat";s:9:"no-repeat";s:8:"position";s:6:"center";}s:8:"advanced";a:5:{s:11:"customclass";s:6:"banner";s:9:"customcss";s:86:".banner{\r\nheight: 340px;\r\n}\r\n.banner h3{\r\npadding-top:3%;\r\nvertical-align: middle;\r\n} ";s:7:"padding";a:4:{s:3:"top";s:0:"";s:5:"right";s:0:"";s:6:"bottom";s:0:"";s:4:"left";s:0:"";}s:6:"margin";a:4:{s:3:"top";s:0:"";s:5:"right";s:0:"";s:6:"bottom";s:0:"";s:4:"left";s:0:"";}s:6:"anchor";s:0:"";}}s: