(367, 1, '2016-03-15 11:19:48', '2016-03-15 11:19:48', '\n\nHandling and Installation\n																						Our services run deep and are backed by over ten years of experience.\n\nHandling\n																						Our services run deep and are backed by over ten years of experience.\n\n<img src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Picture10-300x205.png" width="481" height="329" />\n\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nulla quam velit, vulputate eu pharetra nec, mattis ac neque. Duis vulputate commodo lectus, ac blandit elit tincidunt id. Sed rhoncus, tortor sed eleifend tristique, tortor mauris molestie elit, et lacinia ipsum quam nec dui. Quisque nec mauris sit amet elit iaculis pretium sit amet quis magna. Aenean velit odio, elementum in tempus ut, vehicula eu diam. Pellentesque rhoncus aliquam mattis. Ut vulputate eros sed felis sodales nec vulputate justo hendrerit. Vivamus varius pretium ligula, a aliquam odio euismod sit amet. Quisque laoreet sem sit amet orci ullamcorper at ultricies metus viverra. Pellentesque arcu mauris, malesuada quis ornare accumsan, blandit sed diam.\n\nInstallation\n																						Our services run deep and are backed by over ten years of experience.\n\nStep 1																									\n																																		Gali tempat pipa akan diletakkan sesuai dengan rencana dan pastikan pada dasar galian tidak terdapat batu\n\n<img width="300" height="144" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/instalasi-pipa-1-b.png" />																					\n\nStep 2																									\n																																		Taruh pasir di atas tanah sekitar 5 cm sebagai alas tempat pipa akan diletakkan, lalu dipadatkan  \n\n<img width="300" height="149" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/instalasi-pipa-2-b.png" />																					\n\nStep 3																									\n																																		Letakkan pipa ditempat yang direncanakan\n\n<img width="300" height="147" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/instalasi-pipa-3-b.png" />																					\n\nStep 4																									\n																																		Taruh pasir hingga 1/3 – 2/3 dari diameter pipa – tergantung dari tipe yang diusulkan konsultan (Unsupported, Haunch Supported, atau Side supported), lalu padatkan pasir pada sisi pipa\n\n<img width="300" height="148" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/instalasi-pipa-4-b.png" />																					\n\nStep 5																									\n																																		Timbun sisa galianpipa dan padatkan kembali.Bilamana pipatertanam di posisi yang cukup dalam, sebisa mungkin pemadatan dilakukan setiap40 – 60 cm\n\n<img width="300" height="143" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/instalasi-pipa-5-b.png" />																					\n\n', 'Handling', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '127-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-15 11:19:48', '2016-03-15 11:19:48', 'a:4:{s:7:"post_id";i:127;s:9:"post_hash";s:44:"layers_page_90818dd3359f322148b6193ae30baea2";s:10:"post_title";s:8:"Handling";s:11:"widget_data";a:1:{s:23:"obox-layers-builder-127";a:9:{s:23:"layers-widget-column-12";a:4:{s:6:"design";a:6:{s:6:"layout";s:12:"layout-boxed";s:9:"liststyle";s:9:"list-grid";s:6:"gutter";s:2:"on";s:5:"fonts";a:3:{s:5:"align";s:11:"text-center";s:4:"size";s:6:"medium";s:5:"color";s:7:"#ffffff";}s:10:"background";a:4:{s:5:"color";s:0:"";s:5:"image";s:59:"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/1.jpg";s:6:"repeat";s:9:"no-repeat";s:8:"position";s:6:"center";}s:8:"advanced";a:5:{s:11:"customclass";s:6:"banner";s:9:"customcss";s:88:".banner{\r\nheight: 400px;\r\n}\r\n.banner h3{\r\npadding-top:40px;\r\nvertical-align: middle;\r\n} ";s:7:"padding";a:4:{s:3:"top";s:0:"";s:5:"right";s:0:"";s:6:"bottom";s:0:"";s:4:"left";s:0:"";}s:6:"margin";a:4:{s:3:"top";s:0:"";s:5:"right";s:0:"";s:6:"bottom";s:0:"";s:4:"left";s:0:"";}s:6:"anchor";s:0:"";}}s:5:"